FuncDef: The display aaa online-fail-record dhcp statistics command displays statistics about user login failures.
ExtraInfo:
To check user login failure records, run the display aaa online-fail-record dhcp statistics command. Login failure records of the following types of users are supported:
DHCPv4: Layer 2 DHCPv4 users, Layer 3 DHCPv4 users, Layer 2 IPv4 web users (dial-in through DHCPv4), Layer 2 IPv4 leased line users (dial-in through DHCPv4), and IPv4 802.1X users.
DHCPv6: Layer 2 common DHCPv6 users, Layer 2 IPv6 web users (dial-in through DHCPv6), Layer 3 DHCPv6 users, and IPv6 802.1X users.
